{"tid":668892,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"交友app搞左條女，但唔想拍拖點講先好落台？","createTime":"2018-05-18T04:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T19:21:00.000Z","uid":19218,"like":14,"dislike":214,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"7b3ef5e1a6c4412539a1bd57a2cab7ae3ace870a","tid":668892,"uid":19218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:16:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的，最近係交友app識左個女仔，大家幾啱傾。<br />\n<br />\n上星期食過一次飯，琴晚出黎飲野，飲左兩杯酒，你情我願下搞左。<br />\n<br />\n今日傾起，我話唔想拍拖，佢問琴晚係咪要當無發生過？<br />\n<br />\n點回應會好睇啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7088746e4ab67ecc229a24b33d02a23a08ba56","tid":668892,"uid":92611,"like":228,"dislike":3,"score":225,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:17:49.000Z","msg":"當人係雞就直接講 男人老狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdaeb41ff3d12debd5e418f8244a4654f08122e2","tid":668892,"uid":176427,"like":123,"dislike":1,"score":122,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:17:55.000Z","msg":"俾佢搞返一次<br />\n打和，super~"},{"pid":"60af3e4d61f65342e73299a9c11929c23fdee94c","tid":668892,"uid":2566,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:18:39.000Z","msg":"直接講，有咩問題？"},{"pid":"e1c429a7ab4cf4a559ad4bfc14560ffaa3529f27","tid":668892,"uid":25260,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"60af3e4d61f65342e73299a9c11929c23fdee94c","tid":668892,"uid":2566,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:18:39.000Z","msg":"直接講，有咩問題？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:19:18.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"c92f7b82e5d138dc7f028e1724a0a18dbb0afd84","tid":668892,"uid":166792,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:19:34.000Z","msg":"咪直接話係 你仲想點答佢"},{"pid":"191c247498405e68756949d5b2a4de153624b005","tid":668892,"uid":19218,